^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|This is my sixth lesson on defense 202. It will be similar in format to last week's lesson, as will be weeks seven and eight. The first four weeks I gave you the fundamentals of defense--opening leads, carding, signaling, and counting. I suggest you keep reviewing those principles as they are essential to your becoming a good defender. |
