NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Back to spectacular opening leads. So, people who look for spectacular opening leads tell you how brilliant they are but they fail to mention that for every success, their spectacular opening leads fail four or five times. Therefore, my philosophy is use the fundamentals. They greatly increase the probability that you will be successful in the long run. That is true in most sports and competitive endeavors. The people who are the most successful are those who apply the fundamentals. For the next several tricks let us only look at East's hand. |
