pc|D9|NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Based on his count, West should duck again. Unlike last week, this duck probably makes no difference. With two Kings on the board, there is probably an entry to run the diamonds anyway. Last week, dummy had no outside entries, so knowing how many times to duck the Ace was very important. But this week, it will not likely make any difference at this stage.|
