NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|This example is more typical of how you signal in NT in real life. Some people play a complicated system of suit preference known as Lavinthal discards, particularly in NT. But, I do not particularly like that system. I don't want to get into it here, but if someone has a question about it, feel free to email me, and I will explain how it works and why I don't like it.|
